Radiant Aura and Suggested Environments
A palpable aura of divine protection and stoicism surrounds this character, manifesting as a soft, golden radiance that emanates from the core of his armor and weaponry. Given his heavy, ornate plate and regal colors, he would look most at home standing at the gates of a sprawling, high-fantasy citadel at dawn, where the rising sun could catch the golden accents of his gear. Alternatively, he would suit a darkened, ancient cathedral interior, where the inner glow of his shield and hammer would provide the only light against a backdrop of stained glass and stone pillars. His presence is that of a "God of the Frontlines," a sentinel who remains immovable even when the very world around him begins to crumble.




